item.description: Biography I’m a passionate software developer, leveraging new and proven technologies and practices to deliver high quality solutions. My technical expertise includes cross-platform proficiency, various programming languages, and advanced knowledge of software development methodologies, developer tools and industry best practices. My hands-on experience with a wide range of technologies, enables me to advise and implement the best solution for our client’s problems.
